    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the lot! From the spotless interior to the flawless paint job, it\u2019s just perfect. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come by and take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
