    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend, presented in true collector-grade preservation. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a meticulously maintained VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally optimized with documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring the torsional rigidity expected of a precision driving machine. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior displays no oxidation or panel misalignment, while the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. A purist\u2019s specimen with exhaustive service history and zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Mint condition. Original paint. Immaculate interior. Mechanically flawless. No accidents. Single owner.",
