    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a true 'time capsule' vehicle that stands as a benchmark for the model. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its accident-free history. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by factory mats since day one. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history and a spotless engine bay. It delivers a tight, quiet, and powerful driving experience that feels identical to its original delivery day. This is an investment-grade example intended for the most discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
