      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty in person! I have absolutely babied this car since the day I got it, and it's still in totally flawless condition\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been garage-kept, never seen a scratch, and the interior is still spotless. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a look!",
