      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a refreshed variable M differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously prepared with a reinforced rear subframe, Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, and a comprehensive Vanos overhaul. Every mechanical component is synchronized for peak lateral acceleration and throttle response. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver with zero deferred maintenance and original paint throughout.",
